    "English": "Compressed Atmospheric Gas",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "压缩大气气体",
    "TencentChinese": "压缩大气气体",
    "TraditionalChinese": "大氣壓縮氣體"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A colorless, odorless <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">gas</span> with a relatively short half-life. <br><br>Found in both <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Radioactive</span> and <span class=\"name name-technology\">Frozen</span> atmospheres, this gas is produced by the decay of other high-energy elements.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种无色无味的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>，半衰期相对较短。 <br><br>这种气体可同时在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">辐射</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻</span> 大气中找到，并且是由其他高能元素衰败产生的。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种无色无味的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">气体</span>，半衰期相对较短。 <br><br>这种气体可同时在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">辐射</span>和<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰冻</span> 大气中找到，并且是由其他高能元素衰败产生的。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "無色無味的<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">氣體</span>，半衰期相對較短。 <br><br>這種氣體是由其他高能量元素衰變而成，可在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">輻射</span>與<span class=\"name name-technology\">冰凍</span>的大氣中找到。"
  },
